In his sorrows, Bloodblade noticed a flash on him and suddenly 
focused on it. Void? Pain? What was going on?

Tyrael was curious at what was heppening, when suddenly, a file 
appeared on the screen. The designation made him doubt, then sent a 
chill in his body.

Tyrael: By the Matrix! Darkangel! Drag him out of the base now!
